    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Find the latest month\n\nInstead of hardcoding a date, this Execute Query asks the table itself for the newest `\"YEAR\"`/`\"MONTH\"` — the demo never goes stale.\n\nNote the double quotes: `YEAR` and `MONTH` are **reserved words** in Exasol SQL.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 260
